{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some radios components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a radio with only an indicator, prefer instead "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(isOn:label:additionalLabel:helper:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/body"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Layouts","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing radio indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The radio indicator has two available states:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the radio is filled with a filled circle, the user has made the action to select the radio","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is empty, does not contain anything, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the radio"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The radio can be also outlined in some cases.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}]},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom radio trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}]},{"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":"can be used outside a dedicated picker, thus it does not need any tag and associated type."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, and an additional label but without text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing radio with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  label: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                  helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Rescue from this world!\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related radio as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"]},{"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"See ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/90c467-radio-button","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.1.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Version","style":"note"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}]}],"name":"Since","style":"note"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents13OUDSRadioItemV","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSRadioItem","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}],"roleHeading":"Structure"},"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSRadioPicker":{"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSRadioPicker","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadioPicker","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"A picker allowing to expose several radio buttons and choose only one within the others.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each radio button contains a “tag”, i.e. a supposed to be unique value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker will expose the choosen value through this “tag”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It has also some configuration elements which will override the one applied to nested ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"text":" (divider, read only and error mode, layout and outlined)","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioPicker","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradiopicker","i